Welcome back to The Varsity, my twice-weekly private email about everything=
 that happens off the field and in the executive suites of the sports media=
 business. Call Me Ted, executive produced by cable industry royalty: Dr. J=
ohn Malone, Brian Roberts, and Chuck Dolan. Ted suffers from Lewy body deme=
ntia, and the series has the feel of a decadent homage to the maverick CNN =
founder. For someone like me, who covered Ted in the =E2=80=9990s and aught=
s, the tribute represented a nostalgic tour back in time to the bygone era =
when cable was innovative. It=E2=80=99s worth watching just to see Malone=
=E2=80=99s eyes light up as he recalls a plethora of old Ted stories.

